text.tspan: UK: Share of COVID-19 tests that are positive
Shown is the percentage of people who had a PCR test in the previous 7 days and had at least one
positive test result. Data is currently only shown for regions in England.
Data source: UK Government COVID-19 Dashboard – Last updated 23 April 2023
